      "content": "it's not just about the money though. it's the fact that i promised them everything. i told them i would build something great and now i'm just a walking disaster. every time i think about going back, i just feel this crushing weight... like there's no version of the future where i'm not just a failure. it feels like the only way to actually stop the feeling is to just... not be here anymore.",
